  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">The truth always comes out, but if a Spy gets their hands on it, it will probably end face down in a sewer, in unexplained circumstances. Spies know how to skillfully manipulate those around them and weave a web of lies, so thick and skillfully made that they can even deceive themselves, impersonating to perfection an innocent maid, a queen of merchants or a ruthless mercenary. Spies are the scoundrels who best act in full view, strong in charisma and certain that the mask will fall only if and when they want.</span></p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
